27
00:04:44,369 --> 00:04:46,562
<i>''Molly Mahoney's First. ''</i>

28
00:04:48,457 --> 00:04:51,447
<i>Molly Mahoney was the manager
of the Emporium,</i>

29
00:04:51,647 --> 00:04:55,635
<i>Mr. Magorium's apprentice,
and my only friend.</i>

30
00:04:55,735 --> 00:04:59,124
<i>In the mornings,
Mahoney would play her piano,</i>

31
00:04:59,224 --> 00:05:01,617
<i>attempting to finish
her very first concerto,</i>

32
00:05:01,716 --> 00:05:05,405
<i>but she never could find
the right notes.</i>

33
00:05:15,575 --> 00:05:16,771
