00:15:52,798 --> 00:15:54,400
I am the store manager.

264
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:56,402
Pleasure to meet you.

265
00:15:56,502 --> 00:15:58,804
I have to admit,
when the agency sent me,

266
00:15:58,905 --> 00:16:01,407
I had no idea
that this was a toy store.

267
