This happens every time.

283
00:16:57,668 --> 00:16:59,270
Ah, greetings.
Edward Magorium--

284
00:16:59,370 --> 00:17:00,972
toy impresario,
wonder aficionado,

285
00:17:01,072 --> 00:17:02,273
avid shoe-wearer.

286
00:17:02,373 --> 00:17:04,075
You're here for the
accounting position.

287
00:17:04,175 --> 00:17:05,276
Yes. Henry Weston.

288
00:17:05,377 --> 00:17:06,978
Mm-hmm. Name the
Fibonacci series

289
00:17:07,078 --> 00:17:08,980
