01:19:34,514 --> 01:19:37,114
- Hi.
- Hello.

1429
01:19:38,914 --> 01:19:40,313
Wow.

1430
01:19:40,413 --> 01:19:42,513
What happened in here?

1431
01:19:42,613 --> 01:19:46,613
