by tomorrow morning.

1442
01:20:08,012 --> 01:20:10,013
Okay.

1443
01:20:12,814 --> 01:20:14,215
Do you think I should take it?

1444
01:20:14,315 --> 01:20:16,416
Well...

1445
01:20:16,516 --> 01:20:18,317
Do you think I should take it?

1446
