1453
01:20:40,726 --> 01:20:42,827
And I think
you should keep the store.

1454
01:20:42,927 --> 01:20:44,728
You don't even believe
in this store.

1455
01:20:44,828 --> 01:20:46,529
- No, but...
- I... I can't.

1456
