I want to, but I just can't.

1457
01:20:50,030 --> 01:20:51,331
You ''just'' can't.

1458
01:20:51,431 --> 01:20:55,233
Yeah. I guess not.

1459
01:20:55,333 --> 01:20:57,234
What do you got there?

1460
01:20:57,334 --> 01:20:58,834
Oh, it's the Congreve Cube.

1461
01:20:58,934 --> 01:21:02,936
