1556
01:25:28,152 --> 01:25:30,854
Holy cow.

1557
01:25:30,954 --> 01:25:33,255
What is it?

1558
01:25:33,355 --> 01:25:35,456
A sparkle.

1559
01:26:12,872 --> 01:26:15,273
- Wow!
- Cool.

1560
01:26:49,688 --> 01:26:52,389
Whoa...

1561
01:26:54,090 --> 01:26:57,792
Whoa!

1562
01:28:07,722 --> 01:28:10,023
- I can't believe it.
